task.summary: - Add new interface FRAMEWORK: Antd - Create upload image component - Create the create-car-listing - Add protected routing. If not logged in, the user will be prompted to enter log in details, then will be redirected to the previous page after logging in

- Finished the create-car-listing functionality (logic & interface) - Added basic validation for create-car-listing - Haven't included the error display if there is an error returned with the response from the server
- Change error box component to make it more dynamic

- Create displayCarListing functionality (component + logic) - Add requireAuth to Route - Fixed a CSS issue with Profile.scss - Change base URL of the axios instance so that the URL to call the API can be shortened to "api/xxxx" instead of "http://localhost:9000/api/xxxx"
- Create draft component for display all listings to carOwner

- Almost finish making the showCarListingCollection (component + logic) (update and delete functionality left) - Change "createCarListing" component to "createCar". Add a link to the nav bar to create a new car - Remove the unused CSS files
- Make the "createListingComponent" (component + logic) to correspond to the new API

- Create car editing container + component - Fix the update/delete functionality for car listing - Add a link to navigate between the page to display all car listings and the page to edit a specific car listing
- Make functionality for search bar. - Connect search body (HTML) with the search bar via redux - Change webpack devtool to "cheap-source-map"
